high_descs: Turn around and walk to the two sinks.
Pick up the empty roll of toilet paper between the two sinks.
Turn left and walk to the toilet paper holder by the toilet.
Place the empty roll of toilet paper on the toilet paper holder.
anns.task_desc: Place an empty roll of toilet paper on the toilet paper holder.

high_descs: Turn around and go in front of the sinks.
Pick up the cardboard roll in between the sinks.
Turn left, go to the toilet paper roll holder.
Put the cardboard roll on the toilet paper roll holder.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard roll on a toilet paper roll holder.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink counter.
Pick up the toilet paper tube on the counter between the sinks.
Turn to the left and go to the toilet paper holder.
Put the tube on the toilet paper holder.
anns.task_desc: Put the toilet paper tube on the toilet paper holder.
